name: Which character are you? Tv Show QUIZ
name_original: Which character are you? Tv Show QUIZ
description:
There are many shows on television every day, and each has its different characters who add some value to the storyline. Ever look at the television screen and wonder if there might be a character out there that has the same personality as you? Give it a shot and see who it is

Choose your favorite TV show and Answer 10 Questions And We'll Tell You The Exact TV Character That Make Up Your Personality.

Take this quiz with friends and compare results. Check it out!
